§ METRICS (what-success-looks-like)
  coverage ≥ 85% line + 80% branch via LLVM-sanitizer (stage0) | owned-cov (stage1+)
  mutation-score ≥ 70% via mutation-testing (stage1+)
  fuzz-throughput ≥ 1000 exec/s per-target
  CI-time : fast-suite ≤ 10 min, PR-suite ≤ 45 min, nightly ≤ 4 hours
  regression-sensitivity : catch ≥ 95% of perf/power/correctness-regressions
                            before-merge

∎ TESTING
